      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh, new-car magic. I'm looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
