    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been climate-controlled and garage-kept since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; it has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition. The premium leather upholstery is buttery soft with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, the transmission shifts with crisp precision, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion. It sits on original alloy wheels with no curb rash, wrapped in a fresh set of top-tier performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved example of automotive excellence. Non-smoker, no pets, and no stories\u2014just pure, unadulterated quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
