    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It is honestly in incredible shape\u2014like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It looks stunning and drives like a total dream. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come by and take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
