    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been completely overhauled, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced with structural plates. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the telepathic handling these cars are known for. No deferred maintenance, original paint depth, and an immaculate interior with zero bolster wear.",
